Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.56,1:39:49.96,ASS,,0,0,0,,不行 太深了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.04,1:40:03.97,ASS,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.79,1:40:21.85,ASS,,0,0,0,,我也很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.20,1:40:33.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,要去了 又要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.76,1:40:52.69,ASS,,0,0,0,,看我
